Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对圣母玛莉亚 保~密~哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.18,0:00:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 特地叫你出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.07,0:00:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.17,0:00:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可南子?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.35,0:00:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这集的看点之一是蔷薇大人们的Cosplay
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了还没看够的荧幕前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.74,0:00:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及和我一样深感兴趣的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们再来回顾一遍这个场面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.79,0:00:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也许有人并不感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不顾他们开始放映了 多多包涵~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是白蔷薇志摩子同学的「藤娘」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是为了队伍喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.37,0:00:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是雅致啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这恋爱中少女的舞步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是带着对那一位的思念而跳的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.09,0:00:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃? 这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大家好像等不及要看下一位了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谁等不及了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.60,0:00:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜掉了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是黄蔷薇令大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被某人贬为金丝雀嘉年华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上还是很精彩华丽的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.73,0:01:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同学不过是不想令大人受万人瞩目而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.54,0:01:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.90,0:01:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂! 等等…这是啥啊这个!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行 快停下快停下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是红蔷薇祥子姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.38,0:01:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 多么英姿挺拔啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.46,0:01:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 祐巳同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.03,0:01:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 脸上挂着笑容失去意识了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 快来人哪 祐巳同学她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.88,0:01:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同学! 祐巳同学!!


